high_descs: Head to the bedroom in the front and reach the bed.
Pick up the butterknife from the bed.
Reach the potato on the left of the bed.
Cut the potato on the dresser with the knife.
Put the butterknife on the sidetable.
Pick up a slice of potato from the dresser.
Turn around to head out the bedroom on the right and reach the kitchen across the passage to face the sink.
Wash the potato in water and take it out.
Turn left to head to the round coffeetable in front of the couch.
Put the potato on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed potato on the coffee table.

high_descs: Go ahead straight to the bedroom and next to the bed.
Pick up the butterknife from the bed.
Walk around the potato to its left side, to the white bedstand.
Cut the potato on the bedstand.
Place the butterknife down on the sidetable.
Pick up one slice of potato.
Leave the room the way you came in and go to the kitchen area straight and slightly to the left, going towards the sink.
Rinse the potato off with water and pick it back up.
Leave the kitchen area and turn left, heading towards the small circular coffee table.
Place the potato on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed slice of Potato on a small CoffeeTable.

high_descs: walk down the hall and go in to the bed.
pick up the butterknife from the bed.
walk to the other side of the potato.
go to the nightstand.
Cut the potato with the butterknife on top of the sidetable.
Put the potato down on the nightstand.
Pick up the potato from the sink.
Put the potato in the sink, wash the potato and then remove it.
take the potato to the coffeetable.
Put the potato down on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Go to the CoffeeTable and get the Potato to wash and remove it.
